{"tid":453154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連續殺人肢解魔]日本公寓發現九具屍體，其中兩具被分屍","createTime":"2017-10-31T02:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T16:11:58.000Z","uid":154872,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1428c0c20b5abb310ad7bc1ee4459c68fd29fd","tid":453154,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/31/104158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F104158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4cce588d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">日本神奈川縣座間市一處公寓內，被發生至少有9具屍體，警方已在現場拉起封鎖線。（圖擷自NHK新聞）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔駐日特派員張茂森／東京31日報導〕日本警方在神奈川縣座間市的一處公寓發現其中至少9具屍體，其中包括兩具已經遭到切斷，有2個頭顱被放在冰箱內，警方同時也逮捕一名20歲的男子。<br />\n<br />\n日本警方是在調查在東京八王子市一名23歲的女子失蹤事件，30日晚間在神奈川縣座間60的公寓內一個住戶的冰箱首先發現2個頭顱，其中一個可能是失蹤的女性的頭部。警方在搜查中，以遺棄屍體的罪嫌逮捕了住戶的一名20歲的男子。<br />\n<br />\n日本警方調查，該失蹤女性曾在推特上留言，表示要找可以一起自殺的人，經過警清洗監視器之後，發現該女子曾與疑犯一起步行。<br />\n<br />\n（source：自由時報）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得人驚"},{"pid":"24bb227d6a836ed31a47233c23c1bb047dffcba2","tid":453154,"uid":22858,"like":76,"dislike":20,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字試用版</ins><br />\n<br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<br />\n<br />\n三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n<br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n<br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/442843</a><br />\n<br />\n刺刀捅向習匪頭 鏟平地獄鬼國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439819\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439819</a><br />\n<br />\n【黑暗】濕鳩塞鷗兄已遭連尼住禁言七日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/435231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/435231</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據二：五毛擾亂視聽妖言惑眾</ins><br />\n<br />\nJR：(人手置頂) 屈毛黨名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405731\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405731</a><br />\n<br />\nRedBaron：關愛座呢隻五毛都算高招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451674\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451674</a><br />\n<br />\nGladiclus：（大踢爆）關愛座hunter係5毛！被bam屈毛派親身指證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451720\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451720</a><br />\n<br />\nJR：要求admin立即ban左三位會員︰關愛座hunter, 濕鳩塞鷗, 1000歲人瑞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451747</a><br />\n<br />\nRedBaron（已改名）：香港獨立之後一定要實行獨裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/452801\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/452801</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9d18fd091b2c7aedb7fbf0bc81a1e6bb438310e4","tid":453154,"uid":154872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:50:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06d0862c225018f74ad251595c3cffb879727e22","tid":453154,"uid":93202,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"仲以為又係啲陳年懸案POST <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i